abstract.para: The information in this document is targeted primarily towards the RFPK Software Team and associates and is specific to the computer systems and network installed in the RFPK Laboratory of the &dept; of the &uw;. RFPK is the Resource for Population Kinetics. Its work is supported, in part, by grant P41 EB-001975 of the National Institutes of Health (NIH) of the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services.
